001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007@HistoryLogProps(
008    opCode = 3,
009    displayName = "Basal Rate Change",
010    internalName = "LID_BASAL_RATE_CHANGE",
011    usedByTidepool = true
012)
013public class BasalRateChangeHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
014    
015    private float commandBasalRate;
016    private float baseBasalRate;
017    private float maxBasalRate;
018    private int insulinDeliveryProfile;
019    private int changeTypeId;
020    
021    public BasalRateChangeHistoryLog() {}
022    public BasalRateChangeHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, float commandBasalRate, float baseBasalRate, float maxBasalRate, int insulinDeliveryProfile, int changeTypeId) {
023        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
024        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, commandBasalRate, baseBasalRate, maxBasalRate, insulinDeliveryProfile, changeTypeId);
025        this.commandBasalRate = commandBasalRate;
026        this.baseBasalRate = baseBasalRate;
027        this.maxBasalRate = maxBasalRate;
028        this.insulinDeliveryProfile = insulinDeliveryProfile;
029        this.changeTypeId = changeTypeId;
030        
031    }
032
033    public BasalRateChangeHistoryLog(float commandBasalRate, float baseBasalRate, float maxBasalRate, int insulinDeliveryProfile, int changeTypeId) {
034        this(0, 0, commandBasalRate, baseBasalRate, maxBasalRate, insulinDeliveryProfile, changeTypeId);
035    }
036
037    public int typeId() {
038        return 3;
039    }
040
041    /**
042     * <table border="1">
043     * <caption>Parsed fields for BasalRateChangeHistoryLog:</caption>
044     * <tr><td><code>commandBasalRate</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
045     * <tr><td><code>baseBasalRate</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
046     * <tr><td><code>maxBasalRate</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
047     * <tr><td><code>insulinDeliveryProfile</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 22)</code></td></tr>
048     * <tr><td><code>changeTypeId</code></td><td><code>raw[24]</code></td></tr>
049     * </table>
050     */
051    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
052        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
053        this.cargo = raw;
054        parseBase(raw);
055        this.commandBasalRate = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 10);
056        this.baseBasalRate = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14);
057        this.maxBasalRate = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18);
058        this.insulinDeliveryProfile = Bytes.readShort(raw, 22);
059        this.changeTypeId = raw[24];
060        
061    }
062
063    /**
064     * <table border="1">
065     * <caption>Byte layout for BasalRateChangeHistoryLog.buildCargo(...):</caption>
066     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>
067     * <tr><td>0</td><td><code>new byte[]{3} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
068     * <tr><td>1</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
069     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
070     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
071     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
072     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
073     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
074     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
075     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
076     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
077     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>toFloat(commandBasalRate) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
078     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>toFloat(commandBasalRate) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
079     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>toFloat(commandBasalRate) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
080     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>toFloat(commandBasalRate) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
081     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>toFloat(baseBasalRate) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
082     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>toFloat(baseBasalRate) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
083     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>toFloat(baseBasalRate) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
084     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>toFloat(baseBasalRate) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
085     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>toFloat(maxBasalRate) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
086     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>toFloat(maxBasalRate) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
087     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>toFloat(maxBasalRate) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
088     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>toFloat(maxBasalRate) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
089     * <tr><td>22</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(insulinDeliveryProfile) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
090     * <tr><td>23</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(insulinDeliveryProfile) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
091     * <tr><td>24</td><td><code>new byte[]{(byte) changeType} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
092     * <tr><td>25</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
093     * </table>
094     */
095    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, float commandBasalRate, float baseBasalRate, float maxBasalRate, int insulinDeliveryProfile, int changeType) {
096        return Bytes.combine(
097            new byte[]{3, 0},
098            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
099            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
100            Bytes.toFloat(commandBasalRate), 
101            Bytes.toFloat(baseBasalRate), 
102            Bytes.toFloat(maxBasalRate), 
103            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(insulinDeliveryProfile), 
104            new byte[]{ (byte) changeType, 0 });
105    }
106
107    /**
108     * @return the basal rate which is being changed to
109     */
110    public float getCommandBasalRate() {
111        return commandBasalRate;
112    }
113
114    /**
115     * @return the basal rate which is default for the current profile segment
116     */
117    public float getBaseBasalRate() {
118        return baseBasalRate;
119    }
120
121    /**
122     * @return the maximum allowed basal rate in the profile settings
123     */
124    public float getMaxBasalRate() {
125        return maxBasalRate;
126    }
127
128    /**
129     * @return the ID of the Insulin Delivery Profile (IDP)
130     */
131    public int getInsulinDeliveryProfile() {
132        return insulinDeliveryProfile;
133    }
134
135    public int getChangeTypeId() {
136        return changeTypeId;
137    }
138
139    public enum ChangeType {
140        TIMED_SEGMENT(1),
141        NEW_PROFILE(2),
142        TEMP_RATE_START(4),
143        TEMP_RATE_END(8),
144        PUMP_SUSPENDED(16),
145        PUMP_RESUMED(32),
146        PUMP_SHUT_DOWN(64),
147        ;
148
149        final int id;
150        ChangeType(int id) {
151            this.id = id;
152        }
153
154        public static ChangeType fromId(int id) {
155            for (ChangeType c : values()) {
156                if (c.id == id) {
157                    return c;
158                }
159            }
160            return null;
161        }
162    }
163
164    /**
165     * @return the reason that the basal rate was changed
166     */
167    public ChangeType getChangeType() {
168        return ChangeType.fromId(changeTypeId);
169    }
170    
171}
